                        <interp inst="t18350706-1669-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 27.—
<rs id="t18350706-1669-punishment-53" type="punishmentDescription">
